<p class="ql-align-justify">凭一道“阳山捞鸡”征服老广的挑剔胃</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">皮爽脆、肉厚实、味浓郁</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">有食餮驱车9小时就为了这口鸡味...</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">/在法律允许范围内，活动解释权归品牌所有/</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>01</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">「阳山好鸡汇」靠着一道阳山的正宗鸡味，成功拿下老广的挑剔</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>把整个阳山搬来了广州</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200901/dd179d6471ca448396fcb41547ddf247.gif" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
