<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200901/5d61a313c32a450ea6f7d1042b4e2c3e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200901/6f716372654d425d9a77dbb96d0b4a1f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">以品质食材称霸，是老板最骄傲的一点了！所有的食材，大到鸡鸭鱼肉，小到油米青菜、汤底材料，通通都是从阳山搬运过来的！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200901/a12d38d66eb54f6ba7c0a325f9c042af.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200901/d727969c57984e688def0bd0cba109ea.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">全店头牌阳山鸡，必须是吃粟米、走山路、养足230天的扇鸡，难怪只只都肉质紧实、鲜味爆棚啦。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>吃四道菜，还送牛杂煲</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200901/c9b9e7a0cc6441b9be27d73c242077a3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">一只正宗的阳山鸡，没两张毛爷爷肯定吃不到...</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>02</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>这样吃鸡，仪式感满满</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200901/2c08262b579a449d855222b2ba76c14b.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200901/108ed45d4bf64d4da5aadb5542c25176.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">“捞起捞起，风生水起~”寓意发财发达、风生水起的捞鸡，将家常菜做出了不一样的味道，这就是火出鸡圈的原因。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>一口吃出8种滋味</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200901/1e0507c630fd4aa6af85f6bd7ce2a113.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">捞料是这道菜的灵魂，一盘捞鸡有多达8种配料，诶一口都能尝到新鲜感！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200901/0a3eb4b60e9747df89740e4d78417a2e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200901/70d611f534304e7dae82656d9fae66e2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200901/10db1d98bb97475db2f01f1d2d9e654d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200901/80fd75a09fb34fd9ac0442c4938d523e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200901/eaa93a6fa26344d48cab9f51498866c1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200901/a017b140174a4542b9ddf4b3ef076f50.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200901/0077eaac1f364b8aa428851f70030a48.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200901/1559c5eea5e3459a8754440507a424cb.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">炸芋头丝、红萝卜、白萝卜、鸡汁、炸花生、香菜、姜蓉，还有来自阳山特有的草果叶，8种味道同时在嘴里咀嚼，口感和味蕾双重刺激，妙哇~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>这样捞起，才够风生水起</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200901/aff3071a65ce447ca3c87494cef41cac.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>将鸡肉打散 </strong>去掉鸡头鸡尾后，将鸡肉打散以便捞匀</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200901/bb0d2de1ef444200be5b9474f73c6225.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>加入鸡汁 </strong>蒸鸡体内留存的精华，金灿灿、香喷喷</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200901/a43895792da54d0183912a0b826d7d78.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>加入配料 </strong>依次倒入配料，最后倒入脆口花生提升口感</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200901/c74eede48ac248c79b822298ab2581af.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>捞就对了 </strong>将配料和鸡肉充分地捞在一起</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>啖啖都系“shuo shuo声”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200901/466d4f65093d4604baed16b37326cd17.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200901/108ed45d4bf64d4da5aadb5542c25176.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>阳山好鸡汇</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200901/3cf25263fa804370a5678a4835b9b873.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200901/854379a88ca34f3b941f7c26c9ed5c11.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">捞好后的捞鸡，啖啖都是极品。鸡皮像是打了玻尿酸似的的爽脆Q弹，鸡肉紧实有嚼劲，还飘来阵阵的鸡香味，光是闻都能吃得下两碗大白饭了。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">03</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">解锁更多阳山美食和吃鸡姿势</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">香焖阳山萝卜牛杂煲</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200901/f329adca68f747229b4fe41f82015753.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">这里的牛杂煲跟别处的牛杂煲大有不同，从香油到萝卜，再到牛杂，全是从阳山运来的新鲜食材，确保每一口只有鲜甜。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200901/ec4456ed7ba349b3b5653e075fa680b3.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>香焖阳山牛杂煲</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200901/49a4004b54714619af6a50af71e0a9fb.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200901/55950eb33d794f6aabf48b424cb675fd.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">牛杂软糯又带着韧劲，蘸一口浓郁的酱汁，配上一碗阳山特有的七拱米饭，一口醇正鲜美就此诞生，食肉兽快冲呀！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>鸡杂炒胜瓜</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200901/11ccaddb7070419fb03be9a01b8c9fdc.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200901/3d91dbee885b4157859dfdb2e22bdbb1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200901/13040deb3470418b9493d9c8f43c751e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">在啥都吃的广东人眼里，鸡杂可是个好宝贝~鸡杂炒胜瓜，清甜的胜瓜搭配爽口的鸡杂，口感恰到好处~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>鸡血浸韭菜</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200901/47e5be18433047268d85ece5146633aa.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">这道简单的家常便菜，吃的就是家的感觉。下饭、清肠胃、补充维生素，都是它的标签。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200901/fae68ea408f0449e9cc1c1ff7c7d0420.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">●●●</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">●●●</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200901/b57508f1dfee4cf6b1a90c56654a9b8a.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">选用现宰现煮的阳山鸡血，更加鲜而不腥，嫩得出汁，搭配从阳山运来的韭菜，又是一盘下饭神器了。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>灵芝鸡骨汤</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200901/41547476c9624329b0ffc665971d1e99.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">一年四季都离不开老火靓汤的广东人，这次有口福了！一大煲灵芝鸡骨汤，满满的全是营养，专治广东妈妈的“湿热警告”。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200901/923801f1e3e7401983c3eb2c45d1d04c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">灵芝鸡骨汤</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200901/2b453a9e624e4040823ae521ed352e62.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">香浓鲜美、味道回甘，是这煲汤的精髓。灵芝的药材味与鲜香的阳山鸡搭配，中和了鸡汤的油腻感，还可以吮到鸡骨头的肉，真的一汤多宝了。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">❖</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200901/504dc15c858e46d4ad4c26452d45e7eb.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>阳山好鸡汇（广州店）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">📍店铺地址:</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">广州市荔湾区芳村大道南50号</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">欢聚一堂内右手边</p>
